	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reddidit hic mihi tuas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego vero nunc alia non habeo, quam quae scripsi prius et quę te iam accepisse puto de luctuoso <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliae</placeName> statu.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Tristiora</persName> subinde accipimus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fertur (sed quam firmum hoc sit, nolo affirmare) regem cum 12 equitibus tantum effugisse manus <placeName type="auto_name">Condensis</placeName> et amiralii et venisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetiam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid vero fiat ab illis reliquis, ignoramus adhuc.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causam belli huius alii aliter interpretantur; aliqui nostris culpam dant, ut scripsi proxime; alii dicunt regem publica promulgatione sustulisse edictum pacis et mandasse omnibus evangelicis, ut intra 12 dies regno excedant; hinc illas turbas oriri.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevam</placeName> profugiunt multi inopes, nudi et egeni.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mirum, quod illis a duce <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2478" cert="high">Sabaudię</placeName> transitus conceditur.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugduni</placeName> est misera rerum facies.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man sagt auch, das sich in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Tütschland</placeName> ein groß volk sammle; ire zeichen sigind wyße fänli mitt zweyen zemmengschlagnen henden, trüwwys; nieman aber wüß, wäm si dienen werdind.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ettlich achtend, dem printzen von <placeName type="auto_name">Aurange</placeName>, deßen sun zuͦ <placeName ref="l1322" cert="high">Löwen</placeName> gfangen; ettlich achtend anders.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich hoff, von üch bald etwas zuͦ empfahen.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Was mir dann wirt, wil ich üch auch lon wüßen.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Hiemitt schick ich üch üweren zedel auch wider und dancken üch vast.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Bezae</persName> misi literas, quę ad illum pertinebant, sic etiam d. <persName ref="p8063" cert="high">Steigero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te nostri omnes; saluta tuos quoque omnes meo nomine.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 12. octobris 1567.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[ohannes] Hallerus</persName>, tuus semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, Tigurinae ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo, domino meo semper colendo et compatri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingern</persName> zuͦ Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
